      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7 and boil a kettle</p><p>Add your <strong>basmati rice </strong>to<strong> </strong>an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with<strong> </strong>300ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [390ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[600ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cover tightly with<strong> tin foil </strong>and put the dish in the oven for 30-35 min or until all the water is absorbed and the rice is cooked – this is your <strong>baked rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
