    {
      "instruction": "<p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and chop into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Wash your <strong>pak choi </strong>and slice in half lengthways, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 3,
