    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based,<strong> hob-safe oven-proof casserole dish</strong> with a matching lid with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain your <strong>tofu</strong> and crumble it into large chunks with your fingers directly into the dish</p><p>Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until starting to brown</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
