      "instruction": "<p>Once the tofu has had 15 min, top the dish with the <strong>pak choi halves</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven, covered, for a further 10 min or until the veg is tender – this is your <strong>oven-baked spicy black bean tofu & pak choi</strong></p>",
